<div class="policy-page">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="page-title">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="policy-content">
            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
                <p>We collect information you provide directly when you purchase products, create an account, or contact us. This may include your name, email, shipping address, and payment information.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
                <p>We use the information we collect to:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Process and fulfill your orders</li>
                    <li>Provide customer support</li>
                    <li>Improve our products and services</li>
                    <li>Send you promotional communications (if you opt-in)</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>Data Security</h2>
                <p>We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information. All payment transactions are encrypted using SSL technology.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="policy-section">
                <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
                <p>We may update this privacy policy periodically. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new policy on this page.</p>
            </section>

            <div class="last-updated">
                <p><strong>Last Updated:</strong> @DateTime.Now.ToString("MMMM dd, yyyy")</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
